,"date":"February 23, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Yazid ibn al-\u2018Asamm reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, was asked about the slain at the battle of Siffin. Ali said, \u201cOur slain and their slain are in Paradise, and the matter will be referred to myself and Mu\u2019awiyah at the Reckoning.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 37880\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39873,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/22\/property-blood-haram\/","url_meta":{"origin":37426,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Believers\u2019 property and blood sacred to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 22, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Malik al-Ashja\u2019i reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever declares the unity of Allah and denies whatever is worshipped besides Him, then Allah has made his wealth and life sacred, and his reckoning is upon Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 27213 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39878,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/22\/united-families\/","url_meta":{"origin":37426,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: The Prophet hopes for united families in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 22, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Rifa\u2019ah al-Juhani reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI testify before Allah that no servant dies bearing witness there is no God but Allah and Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah and then does what is right, except that he will find his way\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19393,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/22\/jannah-70000-without-account\/","url_meta":{"origin":37426,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: 70,000 Muslims to enter Paradise without reckoning","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 22, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMy Lord has promised me that seventy thousand from my nation will enter Paradise without reckoning or punishment. Along with every thousand are seventy thousand more, and three more immeasurable groups of His choosing.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2437\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37522,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/15\/families-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":37426,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: The Prophet hopes they join families in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 15, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Rifa\u2019ah al-Juhani reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy the One in whose hand is the soul of Muhammad, no servant has faith and then follows right direction but that he will be admitted into Paradise. I hope they will not enter it unless\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22769,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/04\/27\/reckoning-fully-account\/","url_meta":{"origin":37426,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Hisab: Whoever is interrogated will be punished","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 27, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is fully taken to account on the Day of Resurrection will be punished.\u201d I said, \u201cHas not Allah Almighty said: He will soon have an easy reckoning?\u201d (84:8) The Prophet said, \u201cThat is not the reckoning,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/37426","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=37426"}],"version-history":[{"cou